Question 10 :Implement transformation-based tagging using a set of transformation rules, apply a simple rule
to tag words using python.

Code :
sentence = ["can", "you", "can", "a", "can"]

tags = ["NN"] * len(sentence)

for i in range(1, len(sentence)):
    if sentence[i] == "can" and sentence[i-1] == "you":
        tags[i] = "VB"

print(list(zip(sentence, tags)))

